Chatbot Readme
-----------------------------------------------------------

Requirements
-----------------------------------------------------------
The following programs are required to run this program:

-Python 2.7.8
-NLTK
-Numpy

Extraction
-----------------------------------------------------------
Extract all the files in this zip into a single folder. The
directory structure of this program is important, if a
folder is not setup correctly the program will not run.

Running the Bot
-----------------------------------------------------------
In order to run the chat bot for topic recognition call
chat(). Enter a sentence or word, the program will return
the topic and it's knowledge of that topic. If the topic
is not found in the database then it will attempt to 
determine the topic based on the nouns in the sentence.

Closing
-----------------------------------------------------------
To quit the program enter qqq

